org.petuum.jbosen.row

Interface Row

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DoubleRow, FloatRow, IntRow, LongRow
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DenseDoubleRow, DenseFloatRow, DenseIntRow, DenseLongRow, SparseDoubleRow, SparseFloatRow, SparseIntRow, SparseLongRow

    public interface Row
    This interface specifies a row in a Bosen PS table. An implementation of this interface does not need to be thread-safe.
